Singer Chike Osebuka aka Chike has claimed he has never used the word ” I love you’ on any lady. The claim is shocking considering the songwriter is well known for incessant love songs.   How I was spiritually attacked, by Chinwetalu Agu     Lekki women’s cheating alarming – Sandra Iheuwa     Broke men have no right to chat me – Nkechi Blessing   The 29- year- old said using the word may make him drop his guard. He wrote: “I have never said “I love you’. I guess for me that’s just too vulnerable. I get that feeling that if I say it, my bolz will shrink and maybe disappear. Happy I get to sing it though”.